    "However, the pixel values are easily affected by noise and cannot provide semantic features for cell analysis.",
    "A potentially more effective approach is to adopt a deep CNN model which can learn high-level representations of histology images.",
    "stLearn introduces a deep learning model to extract the image features of spots and integrates them with the spatial location and gene expression.",
    "However, stLearn employs a model pre-trained on natural images which is not fine-tuned for histology images.",
    "In the future, we will incorporate histology images as an additional modality into the SEDR model."
